%
% Final mesh refinement using MMG. Size of the elements depends on the distance to the fault plane
%

****mesher
 ***mesh mesh-remeshed.geof
  **open mesh-before-remeshing.geo
  **adaptation
   *min_size .0005
   *max_size .05
   *verbose   6
   *metric from_file file metric.dat
   *volume_mesher mmg3d
    hgrad 1.25
    hausd 0.01  
    
   *preserve_elsets
    
    ASTHENOSPHERE-70-200-OCEANIC
    ASTHENOSPHERE-70-200-CONTINENTAL
    ASTHENOSPHERE-200-270-OCEANIC
    ASTHENOSPHERE-200-270-CONTINENTAL
    AW
    OCEAN
    CH-0-70
    CH-70-200
    CH-200-270
    CH-270-670
    LITHOSPHERE_CONTINENTAL
    LITHOSPHERE_OCEANIC
    UPPER-MANTLE
    LOWER-MANTLE
    SLAB
    LAYER-54-70-OCEANIC
    
   *preserve_bsets
    fault_plane
    
****return 

